{"type":"message","id":"83af33d3","parentId":"15281136","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:46:24.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来连接失败了。可能是：\n1. WebSocket 服务端没有运行\n2. 端口不对\n3. 网络问题\n\n让我尝试检查一下连接。或者可能需要先启动服务端？但根据 skill 的描述，服务端应该在 LIMO 小车上运行。\n\n让我尝试用默认端口或者检查一下。也可能是服务端还没有启动。\n\n让我直接尝试获取图像，也许服务端已经在运行但端口不对？让我先试试默认的本地地址。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_48a49574348b41589f279029","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/usr/bin/python3 /home/userli/.openclaw/skills/ROS-camera-ws/scripts/camera_ws_client.py --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8766 get_image --camera-topic /usb_cam_0/image_raw --output /home/userli/.openclaw/ros-cam/camera.jpg"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":376,"output":271,"cacheRead":11712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12359,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774154775313}}
